* '''[[小勞勃·道尼|小勞勃·道尼]]''' 飾演 '''[[夏洛克·福爾摩斯|夏洛克·福爾摩斯]]'''，一名[[波希米亞主義|波希米亞]]的科學家及偵探。道尼與他的妻子製片人[[蘇珊·道尼|蘇珊·道尼]]參觀[[喬·西佛|喬·西佛]]的辦公室時，了解了該項目<ref>{{cite news| date = 2008-07-10| title = Robert Downey Jr 'to play Holmes'| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7499055.stm| work = BBC News| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fentertainment%2F7499055.stm&date=2010-01-30| archivedate = 2010-01-30| accessdate = 2010-01-31| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。瑞奇起初認為道尼太老了，由於他想在電影的學習曲線上展現出一個年輕的福爾摩斯，如同《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》。當時最初人選為克里斯汀貝爾，但貝爾因為工作檔期無法配合，因此確定由道尼演出。道尼打算更加關注福爾摩斯愛國的一面和他的[[波西米亞主義|波西米亞主義]]，並認為自己詮釋[[卓別林與他的情人|卓別林]]的經驗為他準備好了英語口音<ref name="bohemian">{{cite news| date = 2008-10-02| first1 = Mark| last1 = Brown| first2 = Ben| last2 = Child| title = Ritchie and Downey Jr launch new, 'authentic' Sherlock Holmes| url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/oct/02/robertdowneyjr| newspaper = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]| publisher = Guardian Media Group| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ffilm%2F2008%2Foct%2F02%2Frobertdowneyjr&date=2010-01-30| archivedate = 2010-01-30| accessdate = 2010-01-30| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。瑞奇覺得他的口音是「無暇」的。道尼為了電影而失去部分的體重，因在與[[克里斯·馬汀|克里斯·馬汀]]聊天時，馬汀建議福爾摩斯看起來應該「憔悴」和「乾瘦」<ref>{{cite news| date = April 2009| title = News Etc.| work = [[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]]| publisher = {{link-en|鮑爾傳媒集團|Bauer Media Group|Bauer Media Group}}| page = 14}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| date = 2009-11-26| author = Bee Wilson| title = The Kitchen Thinker: Sherlock Holmes' diet| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/6661702/The-Kitchen-Thinker-Sherlock-Holmess-diet.html| newspaper = The Telegraph| publisher = [[News_Corporation|News Corporation]]| accessdate = 2010-01-30}}</ref>。

