攝影始於2008年10月<ref name = "start">{{cite news| title = Sherlock Starts Shooting| work = [[IGN_Entertainment|IGN Entertainment]]| publisher = [[News_Corporation|News Corporation]]| date = 2008-10-01| url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/915/915342p1.html| accessdate = 2008-10-03}}</ref>。劇組在[[共濟會大廳|共濟會大廳]]及[[聖保羅座堂|聖保羅座堂]]拍攝<ref name="locations">[http://www.ukonscreen.com/gfbjjkb-Sherlock-Holmes-(2009).html Sherlock Holmes Filming Locations]</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
