== 發行 ==
全球首映禮於2009年12月14日在倫敦舉行，隨後在12月25日於全球上映（英國和愛爾蘭則在26日開始發行），而其原定檔期為11月<ref name="comingsoon" >{{cite news | url = http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=53203 | title = Sherlock Holmes (Warner Bros. Pictures) | work = ComingSoon.net | publisher = {{link-en|CraveOnline|CraveOnline}} | date = 2009-02-25 | accessdate = 2010-01-28 | archive-date = 2009-02-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090226203921/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=53203 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 家庭媒體 ===
在美國，《-{zh-hk:神探福爾摩斯; zh-tw:福爾摩斯; zh-cn:大侦探福尔摩斯;}-》的DVD和藍光/DVD/數位版本於2010年3月30日發布<ref>{{cite web| date = 2010-01-15| first = Chris| last = Bumbray| title = EXCLUSIVE: When will Sherlock Holmes hit DVD?| url = http://www.joblo.com/index.php?id=30426| work = {{link-en|JoBlo.com|JoBlo.com}}| publisher = JoBlo Media| accessdate = 2010-01-31| archive-date = 2010-01-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100123141953/http://www.joblo.com/index.php?id=30426| dead-url = no}}</ref>。截至2011年3月18日，DVD的銷售總額為44,908,336美元<ref>[http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2009/SHOLM-DVD.php Sherlock Holmes – DVD Sales]. The Numbers. Retrieved on 2011-03-18.</ref>。

== 迴響 ==

=== 評價 ===
該片獲得多數影評人的好評。爛蕃茄上收集的230篇專業影評文章中，有162篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為70%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]6.2分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web| title = Sherlock Holmes (Cream of the Crop)| url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sherlock_holmes_2009/?critic=creamcrop| work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]| publisher = {{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}}| accessdate = 2010-01-31}}</ref>，而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的34篇評論文章，其中17篇予以好評，4篇差評，13篇褒貶不一，平均分為57（滿分100）<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web| title = Sherlock Holmes (2009): Reviews| url = http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/sherlockholmes| work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]| publisher = [[CNET_Networks|CNET Networks]]| accessdate = 2010-01-31}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]打出了三顆星（滿分四顆），並稱讚電影中的強大角色、視覺享受和動作情節<ref name="ebert">{{cite web| date = 2009-12-23| authorlink = Roger Ebert| first = Roger | last = Ebert| title = Sherlock Holmes Review| url = http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20091223/REVIEWS/912239991|work=Chicago Sun-Times| accessdate = 2010-01-31}} {{Rating|3|4}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，電影於首週末從3,626家劇院中進帳6,240萬美元的票房，平均每家劇院收穫18,031美元。其成績在該週位居第二，僅次《[[阿凡達|阿凡達]]》（7,560萬美元）。《-{zh-hk:神探福爾摩斯; zh-tw:福爾摩斯; zh-cn:大侦探福尔摩斯;}-》於全球的票房為524,028,679美元<ref name = "mojo"/>，其中美國部分共收入209,028,679美元，使之成為導演蓋·瑞奇在該國最成功的作品<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=guyritchie.htm|title=Guy Ritchie Movie Box Office Results|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2010-09-08|archive-date=2010-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100301160849/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=guyritchie.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 榮譽 ===
2010年1月17日，[[好萊塢外國記者協會|好萊塢外國記者協會]]宣布[[第67屆金球獎|第67屆金球獎]]的得獎者，小勞勃·道尼以飾演福爾摩斯的表現榮獲[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角|金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角]]<ref>{{cite news| date = 2009-12-15| author = [[好萊塢外國記者協會|HFPA]]| title = HFPA — Nominations and Winners| url = http://www.goldenglobes.org/nominations/| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/656OXQnv3?url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/nominations/| accessdate = 2010-01-31| archive-date = 2012-01-31| dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[廣播影評人協會|廣播影評人協會]]將漢斯·季默提名至{{link-en|影評人選擇獎最佳配樂|Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Score|最佳配樂}}，但不敵《[[天外奇蹟|天外奇蹟]]》的[[麥可·吉亞奇諾|麥可·吉亞奇諾]]<ref>{{cite news| date = 2009-12-15| author = [[廣播影評人協會|BFCA]]| title = The BFCA Critics' Choice Awards :: 2009| url = http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2009.php| accessdate = 2010-01-31| archive-date = 2010-10-17| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5tYCgPFpr?url=http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2009.php| dead-url = no}}</ref>。電影於[[第82屆奧斯卡金像獎|第82屆奧斯卡金像獎]]入圍[[奧斯卡最佳原創音樂獎|原創音樂]]和[[奧斯卡最佳藝術指導獎|最佳藝術指導獎]]<ref name="Oscars2010">{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/82nd-winners.html |title=The 82nd Academy Awards (2010) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2013-10-16 |work=''Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences'' |publisher=AMPAS |archivedate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131224033929/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/82nd-winners.html}}</ref>。

